CLAM SAUCE Clam sauce is a topping for pasta , usually linguine .
The two most popular varieties are white , usually featuring minced clams , olive oil , garlic , lemon juice and parsley , or red , usually a thin tomato sauce with minced clams .
Other variants include the incorporation of whole clams , hot pepper flakes and other ingredients .
Clam juice may be used in the preparation of clam sauce .
